AppSettings
===========

General Settings


Example
=======

Setting['key.to.setting']              # => get value(String)
Setting['key.to.setting'] = "my value" # => set value(Any, String as Result)

Configure a router item for manage those settings by your web:

YourApp::Application.routes.draw
  resources :settings
end


